WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.840
Excuse me. Can you tell me the way to Wang Fujing da Ji'er?

00:07.840 --> 00:15.920
Certainly. Go across Dong Chang and Ji'er. Go along the street and turn left at the

00:15.920 --> 00:21.760
third street on the left. It's near here so you can walk there.

00:21.760 --> 00:27.920
Great. And I'd like to buy a guide book about Beijing.

00:27.920 --> 00:34.080
Is there a bookshop near here? Yes. There is a big bookshop over there.

00:34.080 --> 00:40.000
Just along Shi Chang and Ji'er on the right opposite the bank.

00:40.000 --> 00:46.400
Right. Okay. I also want to visit the National Stadium.

00:46.400 --> 00:54.080
How can I get there? Sorry. I'm not sure. Why not ask the policeman over there?

00:54.080 --> 01:00.560
Thank you. You're welcome. You're welcome.

01:00.560 --> 01:08.560
Could you tell me how to get to the National Stadium? Sure. Go along the street

01:08.560 --> 01:14.160
and you'll see an underground station. Take the underground to the Olympic

01:14.160 --> 01:22.240
Sports Center or you can take a bus or a taxi. Thanks a lot. You're welcome.

01:22.240 --> 01:25.040
Have a nice day.

